":"2022-04-16","comment":0,"desc":"今日は球技大会。和泉くんは男子サッカーに、式守さんは女子バレーに出場する。和泉くんは自分が活躍できないとわかっていても、できるだけ頑張ろうとしていた。不幸体質の和泉くんを心配する式守さんだったけど、和泉くんは顔面にボールを受けて失神してしまう。和泉くんは保健室で式守さんに介抱されることになり、2人きりのドキドキの時間を過ごすことに。すると、式守さんは試合に戻らず、ここに残ると言い出して……!?\r\n\r\n脚本：千葉美鈴\r\n絵コンテ：山中祥平\r\n演出：山中祥平、金成旻\r\n総作画監督：渥美智也\r\n作画監督：宮原拓也、降籏秀吉、長尾圭吾、久保茉莉子、板倉健"},{"id":1088210,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1088210","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","duration":"00:23:25","airdate":"2022-04-23","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1088211,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1088211","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","duration":"00:23:25","airdate":"2022-04-30","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1088212,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1088212","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","duration":"00:23:25","airdate":"2022-05-07","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1088213,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1088213","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","duration":"00:23:25","airdate":"2022-05-14","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1088214,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1088214","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","duration":"00:23:25","airdate":"2022-05-21","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1088215,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1088215","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","duration":"00:23:25","airdate":"2022-05-28","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1088216,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1088216","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","duration":"00:23:25","airdate":"2022-06-04","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1088217,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1088217","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"","duration":"00:23:25","airdate":"2022-06-11","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1088218,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1088218","type":0,"sort":11,"name":"","duration":"00:23:25","airdate":"2022-06-18","comment":1,"desc":""},{"id":1088219,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1088219","type":0,"sort":12,"name":"","duration":"00:23:25","airdate":"2022-06-25","comment":0,"desc":""}],"crt":[{"id":101318,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1b/d8/101318_crt_d67FD.jpg","name":"式守","desc":"大西沙織"},{"id":101319,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/14/51/101319_crt_8n548.jpg","name":"和泉","desc":"梅田修一朗"},{"id":104353,"image":"//lain.b